{"tid":883715,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"(阿Sir瞓覺唔使你教) 葵涌2警員疑警車上小睡","createTime":"2018-10-31T04:51:23.000Z","updateTime":"2018-10-31T04:51:23.000Z","uid":184679,"like":1,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":1,"replies":[{"pid":"25559707cb2825272bba50cb50ee0cb1c042d03b","tid":883715,"uid":184679,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-31T04:51:23.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://s.yimg.com/ny/api/res/1.2/84S94ikpLTKogYzebxpUVw--~A/YXBwaWQ9aGlnaGxhbmRlcjtzbT0xO3c9NTAwO2g9NDAwO2lsPXBsYW5l/http://media.zenfs.com/en_us/News/singtao/20181030a160927.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fs.yimg.com%2Fny%2Fapi%2Fres%2F1.2%2F84S94ikpLTKogYzebxpUVw--~A%2FYXBwaWQ9aGlnaGxhbmRlcjtzbT0xO3c9NTAwO2g9NDAwO2lsPXBsYW5l%2Fhttp%3A%2F%2Fmedia.zenfs.com%2Fen_us%2FNews%2Fsingtao%2F20181030a160927.jpg&h=1f84a97d&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n紀律部隊人員一言一行備受市民關注，有網民在Facebook上載圖片，今早見到2名軍裝警員懷疑正在警車上睡覺。警方表示，已知悉有關事件，並正跟進調查。管方非常重視人員的紀律，定必嚴正處理。<br />\n<br />\n有網民&lrm;「黃智聰」在Facebook 「小心駕駛(討論別人駕駛態度)」上載圖片，見到2名警員在一輛警車上，其中一人戴上太陽眼鏡，另一人則合上眼，懷疑閉目養神或小睡片刻。網民見狀，稱「呀sir訓瞓，唔洗你教呀」，地點位於葵涌麗瑤村東華三院高可寧紀念小學外。<br />\n<br />\n照片引起網民議論紛紛，有網民聲稱「警員當更是瞓覺係刑事罪」；有人更譏諷「人哋長期監視黑社會入侵小學行動，野sir做野唔洗你教」、「報警呀！！ 有人暈咗」；但也有人認為，「返工偷懶好正常啫，佢哋都係打份工」。<br />\n<br />\n消息透露，2名警員隸屬葵涌分區巡邏小隊，分區管理層得悉事件後，已召回警署作紀律調查。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.news.yahoo.com/%E8%91%B5%E6%B6%8C2%E8%AD%A6%E5%93%A1%E7%96%91%E8%BB%8A%E4%B8%8A%E5%B0%8F%E7%9D%A1%E7%89%87%E5%88%BB-%E7%B6%B2%E6%B0%91%E8%AD%8F%E8%AB%B7-%E9%98%BFsir%E7%9E%93%E8%A6%BA%E4%BD%BF%E4%BD%A0%E6%95%99-135500333.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.yahoo.com%2F%25E8%2591%25B5%25E6%25B6%258C2%25E8%25AD%25A6%25E5%2593%25A1%25E7%2596%2591%25E8%25BB%258A%25E4%25B8%258A%25E5%25B0%258F%25E7%259D%25A1%25E7%2589%2587%25E5%2588%25BB-%25E7%25B6%25B2%25E6%25B0%2591%25E8%25AD%258F%25E8%25AB%25B7-%25E9%2598%25BFsir%25E7%259E%2593%25E8%25A6%25BA%25E4%25BD%25BF%25E4%25BD%25A0%25E6%2595%2599-135500333.html&d=HetuhokjshoFeYmKQ5or8br9WXPazFMcT8p8rn878U0%3D&h=70a7bf99\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.yahoo.com/%E8%91%B5%E6%B6%8C2%E8%AD%A6%E5%93%A1%E7%96%91%E8%BB%8A%E4%B8%8A%E5%B0%8F%E7%9D%A1%E7%89%87%E5%88%BB-%E7%B6%B2%E6%B0%91%E8%AD%8F%E8%AB%B7-%E9%98%BFsir%E7%9E%93%E8%A6%BA%E4%BD%BF%E4%BD%A0%E6%95%99-135500333.html</a>"}]}